Have you read Freakonomics? If yes, this project is for you. Can you generate freakish insight based on tons of data available at indian government site. For ex you can take Crime Statistics from ______ and analyze it to answer questions like. 

Which state has largest no of Criminals?
Whats the education qualification of rapist?
Are less educated people more likely to be involved in crime aginst women?
Who is more voilent Hindus or Muslim?

and so on...

You will be using pandas and matplotlib.
